'''Jedi Princess''' was a title used to describe both [[Kendalina]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]].<ref name="POTDS">[[Prophets of the Dark Side (novel)|''Prophets of the Dark Side'']]</ref>

[[Canderous Ordo]] called [[Bastila Shan]] a "spoiled Jedi princess," using the term as a pejorative.<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>

